title: Railworks TS2014 vR DB BR103 TEE
description:
virtualRailroads DB BR103 TEE colour / Rhinegold Express coaches

The package includes vehicles used in Germany from 1983 until 1987 for
the Rhinegold Express train.
Two versions of the BR103 in beige-red and 4 coaches in the same colour are included.
